le\nanalysis, customization of the microscopic material parameters and speedup\nratios compared to high-fidelity finite element (HF) simulations.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Fri, 16 Jul 2021 21:10:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-20"}
