ent of radiation shields on the conduction heat load. This analysis is\nconcluded by studying the possibility of using MLI technique in the health\nsector by reducing the evaporation rate of liquid Oxygen during pandemic\nsituations e.g. in COVID19.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sat, 17 Jul 2021 07:55:19 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-07-21"}
